    "description": "Oh No! You broke your broom! Quick, make a bird potion so you can fly to the party tonight. But... you don't know how to make a bird potion. <br><br>Play 4 fun mini games to gather magic ingredients.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/ef3d0831e24f6ddc698ad4fb4d7aecd3.poster.avif?t=1669605212\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/ef3d0831e24f6ddc698ad4fb4d7aecd3.webm?t=1669605212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/ef3d0831e24f6ddc698ad4fb4d7aecd3.mp4?t=1669605212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make different potions and test them to see which animal you make.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/6d4e710ae89255ff4a1c3eab733a7416.poster.avif?t=1669605212\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/6d4e710ae89255ff4a1c3eab733a7416.webm?t=1669605212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151910/extras/6d4e710ae89255ff4a1c3eab733a7416.mp4?t=1669605212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With the help of your trusty pet cat, Guinea Pig, you need to make and test potions until you create a bird. <br><br>Play a rhythm music mini game to gather music magic - click the music notes as the fall in front of potion bottles to &quot;Capture&quot; the magic. Then mix it in to your cauldron to make a potion. Will it make a bird? Test it on Guinea Pig to find out.<br><br>Then play a catch the candy mini game - move your mouse side to side to catch candies in your bottle as they fall - then mix it in to your cauldron to make a potion. Will it make a bird?<br><br>Then play a &quot;keep it up&quot; mini game with a paper airplane - click underneath the airplane to launch it up in the air and try to collect the floating magic items scattered around to &quot;Capture&quot; the magic - Then mix it in to your cauldron to make a potion. Will it make a bird?<br><br>Then play a painting mini game. Follow the bumble bee around the canvas to paint a design. You can also paint whatever you'd like and you have a chance later in the game to paint again if you'd like, with a stencil! When you're done with the mini game, take this new ingredient and mix it in to your cauldron to make a potion. Will it make a bird?",
